{"tid":2302219,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生被控去年聖誕德福廣場襲警 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-11-27T02:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T08:12:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6df616e285d9f489bd9098570dbe0e6b7f588d34","tid":2302219,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11648&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpOTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=0d43022d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11648</a><br />\n#觀塘裁判法院第八庭<br />\n#梁少玲裁判官<br />\n#1225九龍灣 #裁決<br />\n<br />\n陳(17)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n被控於2019年12月25日在德福廣場一期一樓fancl外襲擊警員7100<br />\n<br />\n審訊詳情<br />\n<br />\n結案陳詞<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n審訊概覽：<br />\n兩個控方證人24710及7100皆同意被告人一直以同一速度奔跑，目的是為迴避警員（與襲擊控罪相反）。<br />\n7100報稱受襲警員在盤問下承認，若非自己主動上前截停被告人，被告人並不會與7100碰撞。<br />\n7100在較早前錄取口供從未提及自己手持盾牌，辯方陳芊仲大律師質疑7100是因為知道錄影片段能清晰見到自己手持盾牌。因而改變口供。<br />\n被告人被盾牌撞到後反彈於Fancl玻璃門再跌落地。<br />\n控方強調魯莽行為仍構成襲警，但被告人只希望盡快離開現場，在混亂中或不知道警員有意截停自己，並非魯莽行為。<br />\n<br />\n【速報】<br />\n🎊罪 名 不 成 立🎊"},{"pid":"5101553acaf6eb9ece677cf1338c04917aa55a8e","tid":2302219,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86da16d9a3e13056878ea496e0cbfb532ac2d213","tid":2302219,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6df616e285d9f489bd9098570dbe0e6b7f588d34","tid":2302219,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11648&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpOTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=0d43022d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank